#:<math>\frac{n(n+1)}{2}=\sum_{k=1}^n k < \sum_{k=1}^n \sqrt{k(k+1)} < \sum_{k=1}^n (k+\frac{1}{2}) =\frac{n^2+2n}{2}<\frac{(n+1)^2}{2}</math>{{refn|group=注|这里用了[[等幂求和|等幂求和]]的求和方法}} {{refn|group=参|name=ref3}}
